# CODEOWNERS
#
# This file defines who is automatically requested for review when a PR
# touches specific files or directories.
#
# Syntax:
#   <pattern>  @<owner> [@<owner2> ...]
#
# Patterns follow the same rules as .gitignore.
# The last matching pattern takes precedence.
#
# Reference: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default: all files require review from these owners
*       @OWNER

# Examples (uncomment and customize as needed):
# /.github/         @OWNER             # CI/CD and repo config
# /docs/            @OWNER             # Documentation
# /src/api/         @OWNER @api-team   # API layer
# /src/frontend/    @OWNER @ui-team    # Frontend
